{"tid":430944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港警察超級犯罪聯賽(警超聯)正式開季 (10/10/17-16/1/18)","createTime":"2017-10-10T09:04:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-05T01:41:47.000Z","uid":83097,"like":162,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"498c6af18cbc388f3eb68167dc2d9c598e846bb4","tid":430944,"uid":83097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T09:04:12.000Z","msg":"首先係道講句唔好意思潛左水一排<br />\n呢幾日要返工好唔得閒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n參考左各位巴絲打意見後正式finalize以下賽程同規則 :<br />\n1. 賽季由即日起到16/1/18號連續14個星期<br />\n2. 警超聯參賽隊伍以下為14隊 <br />\n3. 每隊輪流做1個星期主場<br />\n4. 主場球員入波+3分，作客+1分<br />\n5. 球員被投訴成立+5分<br />\n6. 球員入波而隊伍不詳 = 每隊+3分<br />\n6(1) 賽季完結前球員身份被證實 = 該隊+3分<br />\n7. 新聞有&quot;因佔中壓力&quot;/&quot;警方非常重視&quot;/&quot;人員操守&quot;/&quot;高層震怒&quot;/&quot;嚴正處理&quot;或同等意思+3分<br />\n8. 高技術入球(風化/兒童有關/貪污/藏毒/傷人/謀殺/誤殺)額外+5分<br />\n9. 工作間入球+4分<br />\n10. 分數每星期二更新<br />\n11. 賽季內被定罪+2分<br />\n<br />\n參賽隊伍如下 :<br />\n<br />\n1. 重案組<br />\n2. 學警<br />\n3. 要員保護組<br />\n4. 機場特警組<br />\n5. 有組織罪案及三合會調查科<br />\n6. 輔警<br />\n7. 機動部隊<br />\n8. 軍裝警<br />\n9. 退休警察<br />\n10. 毒品調查科<br />\n11. 水警<br />\n12. 衝鋒隊<br />\n13. 商業罪案調查科<br />\n14. 交通警"},{"pid":"1dc0fc580cb2dcf281f6e4609c77845fdd7176bf","tid":430944,"uid":83097,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T09:11:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171010/bkn-20171010132849525-1010_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171010%2Fbkn-20171010132849525-1010_00822_001.html&d=exzgDcy%2FDcOGJU%2F3kcsv9J7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=72df195b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171010/bkn-20171010132849525-1010_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n3 Points have been awarded to each team.<br />\n<br />\n重案組 = 3<br />\n學警 = 3<br />\n要員保護組 = 3<br />\n機場特警組 = 3<br />\n有組織罪案及三合會調查科 = 3<br />\n輔警 = 3<br />\n機動部隊 = 3<br />\n軍裝警 = 3<br />\n退休警察 = 3<br />\n毒品調查科 = 3<br />\n水警 = 3<br />\n衝鋒隊 = 3<br />\n商業罪案調查科 = 3<br />\n交通警 = 3"},{"pid":"6cccce5660656b9b4502317db99f6baa9d14c101","tid":430944,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T16:32:18.000Z","msg":"周二（17日）傍晚6時半左右，有警員在旺角港鐵站巡邏期間，發現一名男子在地鐵站的扶手電梯，懷疑以手提電話偷拍一名女子裙底，遂上前截查，當場將涉案男子拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方最初將案件列作「公眾地方行為不檢」，隨後經經進一步調查，案件改列「破壞公眾體統」，據悉，被捕男子姓朱(26歲)，為一名休班警；被偷拍的女子則27歲。<br />\n<br />\n警方發言人證實，被捕男子為一名休班警務人員，案件交由旺角警區重案組跟進。發言人重申，警隊非常重視人員操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。"},{"pid":"840399bd2dd1bb10b46931007a04cdc11d94fcbc","tid":430944,"uid":5297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T01:02:09.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56724977265093eb36a4c352423df0896ccfd27b","tid":430944,"uid":47565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T01:28:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63f47e1eb79926dc2a538057633ddf9a7a1731d3","tid":430944,"uid":52581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T01:32:11.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aca782350f90f7d4fc64c73407618b16d388946","tid":430944,"uid":14888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T01:38:23.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"876ae7e8ef0f395c65ea87cad446911a1f76aa31","tid":430944,"uid":60070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T01:40:23.000Z","msg":"休班警大熱"},{"pid":"9eec0ac57932eb4875d54709b56a3c9d7ba90f14","tid":430944,"uid":31786,"like