門"},{"pid":"4c53d22e3ac5d2bf9214c973cff2c996918d924f","tid":430944,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T04:11:12.000Z","msg":"休班警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c3e056bcf885d46c01c23ce46ad65095fe8d972","tid":430944,"uid":27909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T04:16:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"777d51ba2e874b4d765cb0e06603d8e0aa3ccab4","tid":430944,"uid":38784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T04:46:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a4be664880d083034be6027fd74cad5b2c1c024","tid":430944,"uid":2101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T05:03:55.000Z","msg":"冇更新過既"},{"pid":"c9fd2fb7f6c6d0daafc830342465778d8f81e264","tid":430944,"uid":23392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T05:12:27.000Z","msg":"冇人?"},{"pid":"d8905877d404c31325ef62a9dc8a912096930594","tid":430944,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T07:48:39.000Z","msg":"1. 賽季由即日起到16/1/18號連續14個星期<br />\n2. 警超聯參賽隊伍以下為14隊 <br />\n3. 每隊輪流做1個星期主場<br />\n<br />\n姐係純粹係每隊各有一個禮拜bonus加多啲分咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我仲以為賽制係單循環1 on 1隻抽添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b13d89b2cfc4f26527d0c7dd3596a7dcc6ff971e","tid":430944,"uid":141879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T09:39:01.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】年輕男警員於去年6月下旬‪至7月8日‬間於油麻地友翔道警署5樓，三度偷竊同袍放置於儲物櫃室內的逾千元現金，同袍見事有蹺蹊，暗中於儲物櫃內安裝閉路電視及記下鈔票編號，始揭發事件，男警員早前承認4項入案犯法罪，練錦鴻暫委法官今指被告犯案有違誠信，是有計劃的行動，行為令警隊蒙羞，今於區域法院被判囚21個月。<br />\n<br />\n　　練官續指，27歲被告劉智偉得到了同僚信任，知道更衣室及其儲物櫃的密碼，更於一個月內干犯4次罪行，證明被告非一時貪心，是長期干犯及有計劃的行為。練官又指，被告身為警員，於市民信任之下得到權利維護法紀，惟被告知法犯法，故判以重刑。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a37420a397509fa9a67be10f9187cacb63af5d57","tid":430944,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T10:04:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">GoodBoysGoodGirls,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHandHand加油！！！</span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"1e7031f41a7be62c747c377fdc8092ad56147a0c","tid":430944,"uid":114798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T10:05:15.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"2670e1c91a23a55514fab0d1b87ae7c0fef6586b","tid":430944,"uid":71345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T11:23:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>【星島日報報道】年輕男警員於去年6月下旬‪至7月8日‬間於油麻地友翔道警署5樓，三度偷竊同袍放置於儲物櫃室內的逾千元現金，同袍見事有蹺蹊，暗中於儲物櫃內安裝閉路電視及記下鈔票編號，始揭發事件，男警員早前承認4項入案犯法罪，練錦鴻暫委法官今指被告犯案有違誠信，是有計劃的行動，行為令警隊蒙羞，今於區域法院被判囚21個月。<br />\n<br />\n　　練官續指，27歲被告劉智偉得到了同僚信任，知道更衣室及其儲物櫃的密碼，更於一個月內干犯4次罪行，證明被告非一時貪心，是長期干犯及有計劃的行為。練官又指，被告身為警員，於市民信任之下得到權利維護法紀，惟被告知法犯法，故判以重刑。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪8號？"},{"pid":"52ecb56c74c950726a00bf8652cc5f20de1af5df","tid":430944,"uid":129202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T11:32:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a921021256f3fa8c1dc05194d1cc14e9b0d68f6","tid":430944,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T11:33:13.000Z","msg":"借個位黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-lar